      "para_id": "Q004133.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Amar-Suena , king of the four quarters , the beloved of Inana : Lugal-engardug , steward of Inana , nueša - priest of Enlil , child of Enlil-amah , steward of Inana , nueša priest of Enlil , is your servant ."
    }
  ],
